/batman_v_superman_dawn_of_justice/|title=Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice |publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]]|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=December 8, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 44 (51 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice |title=Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice (2016): Reviews|publisher=[[CBS]]|work=[[Metacritic]]|accessdate=July 18, 2008}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{sort grade|B}}<ref name=\"Bcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Batman: The Killing Joke''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 40% (5.66/10 average rating) (40 reviews)<ref name=\"killingjokeRT\">{{cite web | url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_the_killing_joke/ | title=Batman: The Killing Joke (2016) | publisher=[[Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate=October 26, 2019}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\"|\n| style=\"background:#d3d3d3;\" data-sort-value=\"Z\" |\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Lego Batman\" | ''The Lego Batman Movie''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 90% (7.53/10 average rating) (306 reviews)<ref name=rotLego>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lego_batman_movie|title=The Lego Batman Movie (2017)|work=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=December 8, 2017}}</ref> \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|75 (48 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-lego-batman-movie|title=The Lego Batman Movie reviews |work=Metacritic|accessdate=February 5, 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{sort grade|A\u2212}}<ref name=\"Bcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Justice League''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 40% (5.26/10 average rating) (387 reviews)<ref name=\"rotJL\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/justice_league_2017|title=Justice League (2017)|work=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=September 2, 2019}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 45 (52 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/justice-league|title=Justice League Reviews|work=Metacritic|accessdate=December 8, 2