/dcuam/publicenemies/backstage/conroy.php|title=The World's Finest - DC Universe - Superman / Batman: Public Enemies|website=dcanimated.com|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* 2010: ''[[Justice League: Crisis on Two Earths]]'', a loose adaptation of various DC comics with [[William Baldwin]] voicing Batman<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://animesuperhero.com/william-baldwin-on-voicing-the-dark-knight-for-justice-league-crisis-on-two-earths/|title=William Baldwin on Voicing the Dark Knight for \"Justice League: Crisis on Two Earths\"|last=Liu|first=Ed|date=2009-12-17|website=Anime Superhero News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* 2010: ''[[Superman/Batman: Apocalypse]]'', based on ''Superman/Batman: The Supergirl from Krypton'' with Kevin Conroy voicing Batman<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.comicbookmovie.com/superman/kevin-conroy-interview-superman/batman-apocalypse-a22734|title=Kevin Conroy Interview: Superman/Batman Apocalypse|last=Under: \"Superman\"|first=EdGross {{!}} 9/17/2010 Filed|website=www.comicbookmovie.com|language=en-us|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* 2010: ''[[DC Super Friends|DC Super Friends: The Joker\u2019s Playhouse]]'', based on the [[Fisher-Price]] toyline with [[Daran Norris]] voicing Batman<ref name=\":2\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.voiceoverherald.com/many-voices-batman/|title=The Many Voices of Batman -|date=2014-10-20|website=Voice Over Talent Industry News|language=en-US|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* 2012: ''[[Justice League: Doom]]'', based on ''[[JLA: Tower of Babel]]'' with Kevin Conroy voicing Batman<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2599353/justice-league-doom-cast-nathan-fillion-kevin-conroy/|title='Justice League: Doom' Cast Includes Nathan Fillion, Kevin Conroy|last=Page|first=Splash|website=MTV News|language=en|access-date=2019-12-01}}</ref>\n* 2013: ''[[Justice League: The Flashpoint Paradox]]'', based on ''[[Flashpoint (comics)|Flashpoint]]'' with [[Kevin McKidd]] voicing Batman<ref name=\":2\" />\n* 2014: '