ico Zacatepec|Zacatepec]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=Marcos Montiel|pos=MF|other=at [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Zacatepec|Zacatepec]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=Iv\u00e1n Moreno|pos=MF|other=at [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Zacatepec|Zacatepec]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Manuel P\u00e9rez Ruiz|Manuel P\u00e9rez]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Mineros de Zacatecas|Zacatecas]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Francisco Israel Rivera|Francisco Rivera]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Atlante F.C.|Atlante]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Carlos Rosel]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Celaya F.C.|Celaya]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=Giovanni Soto|pos=MF|other=at [[Club Atl\u00e9tico Zacatepec|Zacatepec]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=Juan Hern\u00e1ndez|pos=FW|other=at [[Saltillo F.C.|Saltillo]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Ricardo Mar\u00edn]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Celaya F.C.|Celaya]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Diego Pineda]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Atl\u00e9tico San Luis]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014|nat=MEX|name=[[Alfonso Emilio S\u00e1nchez|Alfonso S\u00e1nchez]]|pos=FW|other=at [[Club Tijuana|Tijuana]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Reserve teams===\n{{Main|Club Am\u00e9rica Reserves and Academy|l1=Am\u00e9rica Reserves and Academy}}\n\n===Notable players===\n\n====Historic players====\nAs part of Club Am\u00e9rica's centenary celebrations in 2016, a public vote was taken via the club's website in which the following players were chosen as 'Historic Players'. Players whose names appear ''italicized'' played for the club at the time the votes were taken.\n\n;Goalkeepers<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.clubamerica.com.mx/comunicados/homenaje-porteros-historicos-america/|title=Homenaje a porteros hist\u00f3ricos de Am\u00e9rica * Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Official|date=2016-07-15|work=Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Oficial|access-date=2017-03-09|language=es-ES}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Guillermo Ochoa]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} ''[[Mois\u00e9s Mu\u00f1oz]]''\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Adolfo R\u00edos]]\n* {{flagicon|ARG}} [[H\u00e9ctor Zelada]]\n\n;Defenders<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.clubamerica.com.mx/aficionados-2/homenaje-los-defensas-historicos-del-america/|title=Homenaje a los defensas hist\u00f3ricos del Am\u00e9rica * Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Oficial|date=2016-07-31|work=Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Oficial|access-date=2017-03-09|language=es-ES}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Alfredo Tena]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Mario Trejo (footballer)|Mario Trejo]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Armando Manzo]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Juan Hern\u00e1ndez (footballer)|Juan Hern\u00e1ndez]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Jos\u00e9 Antonio Castro]] \n* {{flagicon|URU}} [[Cesilio de los Santos]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} Vinicio Bravo\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Duilio Davino|Dulio Davino]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Miguel Lay\u00fan]]\n\n;Midfielders<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.clubamerica.com.mx/comunicados/homenaje-mediocampistas-historicos-azulcremas/|title=Homenaje a mediocampistas hist\u00f3ricos Azulcremas * Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Oficial|date=2016-09-18|work=Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Oficial|access-date=2017-03-09|language=es-ES}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[Daniel Brailovsky]]\n* {{flagicon|CHI}} [[Carlos Reinoso]]\n* {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ant\u00f4nio Carlos Santos]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[P\u00e1vel Pardo]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Germ\u00e1n Villa]]\n* {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Eduardo Bacas]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} Gonzalo Farf\u00e1n\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Alfredo S\u00e1nchez (footballer, born 1904)|Alfredo S\u00e1nchez]]\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Crist\u00f3bal Ortega]]\n* {{flagicon|ZAM}} [[Kalusha Bwalya]]\n* {{flagicon|PAR}} ''[[Osvaldo Mart\u00ednez]]''\n* {{flagicon|ARG}} ''[[Rubens Sambueza]]''\n\n;Forwards<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.clubamerica.com.mx/comunicados/estos-los-delanteros-historicos-elegidos-nuestra-aficion/|title=Estos son los delanteros hist\u00f3ricos elegidos por nuestra afici\u00f3n * Club Am\u00e9rica - Sitio Oficial|date=2016-10-05|wor